Analyzing LotArea

Definitions : Lot size in square feet
There are 14 outliers whose value are greater than 50000 feat squares, I set the limitation of the plot on 50000. The maximum value is 200000.
In general, we would assume that the size of lot is highly correlate with the sale price. Nonetheless, the stength correlation does not support this hypothesis.After all, the relationship between size of Lot and sale price is positive.
